  "detailed_description": "<strong>Crazy Drift</strong> It is an incredibly realistic and high-fidelity drifting, racing and driving game that smoothly simulates the body physics engine in every component of the car resulting in very accurate realistic behavior. Live the fun life with real driving and enjoy the realism of the crushing system<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Maps<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/ab22e965f2a465d23a8f62d5b269fe66.avif?t=1703943865\" width=552 height=270 /></span><br><br><strong>Body Physics:</strong> We have designed the car with high precision, huge amounts of fine detail, and a realistic physics system where the car collision is incredibly accurate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/8fcf8776498616bf08f4157b5570fe4e.poster.avif?t=1703943865\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/8fcf8776498616bf08f4157b5570fe4e.webm?t=1703943865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/8fcf8776498616bf08f4157b5570fe4e.mp4?t=1703943865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Cars:</strong> We have many cars such as ( Drift Car, Motorbike, racing car, stock car, truck) <br>We will also add more cars in the future.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/d26d36700239d1235d49a3dbb2e9368c.poster.avif?t=1703943865\" width=546 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/d26d36700239d1235d49a3dbb2e9368c.webm?t=1703943865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/d26d36700239d1235d49a3dbb2e9368c.mp4?t=1703943865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Crazy Drift</strong> It is an incredibly realistic and high-fidelity drifting, racing and driving game that smoothly simulates the body physics engine in every component of the car resulting in very accurate realistic behavior. Live the fun life with real driving and enjoy the realism of the crushing system<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Maps<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/ab22e965f2a465d23a8f62d5b269fe66.avif?t=1703943865\" width=552 height=270 /></span><br><br><strong>Body Physics:</strong> We have designed the car with high precision, huge amounts of fine detail, and a realistic physics system where the car collision is incredibly accurate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/8fcf8776498616bf08f4157b5570fe4e.poster.avif?t=1703943865\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/8fcf8776498616bf08f4157b5570fe4e.webm?t=1703943865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/8fcf8776498616bf08f4157b5570fe4e.mp4?t=1703943865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Cars:</strong> We have many cars such as ( Drift Car, Motorbike, racing car, stock car, truck) <br>We will also add more cars in the future.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/d26d36700239d1235d49a3dbb2e9368c.poster.avif?t=1703943865\" width=546 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166990/extras/d26d36700239d1235d49a3dbb2e9368c.